node.text: Movie theater-quality popcorn, right from your countertop. What could be better?! Maybe a little butter on top (duh), which, thanks to the built-in warming tray up top, will be perfectly melted as the popcorn pops. Make every night movie night at the link in bio. 📸: @mj_kroeger

node.text: Our Saturday night plans consist of cuddling up on the couch with a bowl of @whisperofyum's chicken congee with jammy eggs, fried shallots, and chili oil. Find her recipe at the link in bio. #f52community #f52grams

node.text: Friends, it brings us great pleasure to say we have another 🔥 recipe from our Resident @woon.heng to share with you! Her Jian Dui are deep-fried, which brings out the aroma and crunch of the sesame seeds, and, thanks to the rice flour, the texture is as soft as can be. Head to the link in bio to try the recipe. #f52community
